  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\">Pheasants seem to live a double life. When they are away from home and in the midst of other creatures they are fearful, always on edge and ready to react to any threat, real or imaginary that it may be; they seem to be in a hurry to resolve their business as quickly as possible, and do not trust the overwhelming majority of the people they have to deal with they are unfriendly, suspicious and brusque. Once they return to their home, however, they change radically: friendly, affable, charismatic and confident, they become jovial hosts and lovers of good living, able to brilliantly entertain tables of adoring guests. Pheasants are greedy, materialistic, a little superficial and secretly ambitious, but not evil. The social evenings organized by them are well known for the delicacy of the food (the demanding palate of these Ruspei is equally famous), the opulence of the setting and the quality of the guests, generally all<br />highly visible individuals carefully selected by the hosts, who love surrounding themselves with friends and acquaintances of prestige and enjoy their fame.</span> <br style=\"font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;line-height:normal;text-align:-webkit-auto;text-size-adjust:auto\" /></span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><em><strong>I</strong></em></span><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><em><strong>ncrease in Ability Scores.</strong></em> </span><span class=\"fontstyle2\">Your  <span class=\"fontstyle0\">Constitution </span>score increases by 2 and your  <span class=\"fontstyle0\">Wisdom </span>score increases by 1.<br /></span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><em><strong>Age.</strong></em> </span>A Ruspei reaches maturity around the age of 14 <span class=\"fontstyle0\">and is immediately considered independent. They have an average lifespan of around 60 years.</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><em><strong>Speed. </strong></em></span></span>Your base speed on the ground is 25 feet, and your <span class=\"fontstyle0\">flying speed is 30 feet.</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><em><strong>Size. </strong></em></span>A Pheasant can reach a height of between 3 1/2 feet <span class=\"fontstyle0\">and 4 1/2 feet, and weigh between 65 lbs and 90 lbs</span>. Your size is Medium. The male specimens of Ruspei are on the average larger <span class=\"fontstyle0\">than females.</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><em><strong>Wild spirit.</strong></em> </span><span class=\"fontstyle2\">You have proficiency in survival skills.</span> <br style=\"font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;line-height:normal;text-align:-webkit-auto;text-size-adjust:auto\" /></span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><span class=\"fontstyle2\">@Compendium[world.species-features.ZLta2Wjm3OsgNAk0]{Wings}</span></span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><span class=\"fontstyle2\">@Compendium[world.species-features.DO8bJUsTURvkwDVu]{Pecking}</span></span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><span class=\"fontstyle2\">@Compendium[world.species-features.9ALHHLuQoSWQRqN4]{Prehensile Legs}</span></span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><span class=\"fontstyle2\">@Compendium[world.species-features.plFixBkurLVhc8dv]{Acute Hearing}</span></span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><span class=\"fontstyle2\"><span class=\"fontstyle2\">@Compendium[world.species-features.f8BD0svXngQPjPsa]{Careful}</span></span></span></p>\n<p>@Compendium[world.species-features.DXFYqjVUtn7isXQ0]{Rural Bond}</p>\n<p>@Compendium[world.species-features.ZRadhCkmL5C2sXjX]{Limited Flight}</p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle2\">@Compendium[world.species-features.NT1pq3nHCIdCuQhJ]{Protective}</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle3\"><em><strong>Instinct of Familia, Habits (Prey):</strong></em> </span><span class=\"fontstyle4\">“I appreciate the daily routine and I am averse to change”.</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle4\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><em><strong>Instinct of Species, Hedonist:</strong></em> “</span><span class=\"fontstyle2\">I devour, consume and savor everything I encounter”.</span> <br style=\"font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:normal;orphans:2;text-align:-webkit-auto;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px\" /></span></p>",
      "chat": "",
      "unidentified": ""
    },
    "source": "Historia Manuale pagina: 115",
